	"general": {
		"title": "Sankey Plot [SPAC] [DMAP]",
		"instructions": "Generates a static and an interactive Sankey plot to visualize annotation relationships.  A relationship is defined as a unique pair of values, one from the source annotation and one from the target annotation.\\\nPlease refer to DUET Documentation and GitHub Documentation for further information."
	},
